<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Inbox Note Card 设计探索 | atelier</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          fontFamily: {
            display: ['Playfair Display', 'serif'],
            sans: ['Inter', 'sans-serif'],
          },
          colors: {
            atelier: {
              cream: '#fafaf5',
              forest: '#2d5a3d',
              lime: '#c8e64a',
              surface: '#f9f9f9',
              surfaceLow: '#f3f3f3',
              onSurface: '#1a1c1c',
              onSurfaceVariant: '#444840',
              outlineVariant: '#c4c8bd',
              primaryFixed: '#d3e9c3',
            }
          },
          boxShadow: {
            'card': '0 2px 24px rgba(26, 28, 28, 0.04)',
            'card-hover': '0 8px 32px rgba(26, 28, 28, 0.08)',
            'glass': '0 8px 32px rgba(45, 90, 61, 0.12)',
            'paper': '0 4px 20px rgba(45, 90, 61, 0.08)',
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
  <style>
    .phone-frame {
      box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }
    .scrollbar-hide::-webkit-scrollbar {
      display: none;
    }
    .scrollbar-hide {
      -ms-overflow-style: none;
      scrollbar-width: none;
    }
    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-6px); }
    }
    .animate-float {
      animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    .animate-float-delayed {
      animation: float 4s ease-in-out 2s infinite;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-atelier-cream text-atelier-onSurface font-sans">

  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="border-b border-atelier-outlineVariant/30 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm sticky top-0 z-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-5">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <div>
          <h1 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-atelier-forest">Inbox Note Card</h1>
          <p class="text-sm text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant mt-1">设计探索 — 增强显示效果与色彩表达</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant">
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-atelier-primaryFixed text-atelier-forest font-medium">8 种方案</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-atelier-outlineVariant">Native iOS</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-10">

    <!-- Intro -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-atelier-forest mb-3">设计目标</h2>
        <p class="text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant leading-relaxed">
          当前的 Inbox 卡片以白色为底、左侧淡绿色装饰条为主，整体较为素雅。为了提升视觉层次感与品牌识别度，
          我们探索了 <strong>8 种不同的设计方向</strong>，核心围绕两点展开：
          <span class="text-atelier-forest font-medium">增强显示效果</span> 与
          <span class="text-atelier-forest font-medium">为卡片注入色彩</span>。
          每种方案都保留了卡片的信息层级，但在色彩运用、材质感和空间表现上各有侧重。
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Designs Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-10">

      <!-- 1. Baseline -->
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-atelier-forest">01. Baseline 现状</h3>
          <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-gray-100 text-gray-600">当前版本</span>
        </div>
        <div class="phone-frame rounded-[40px] border-[8px] border-white bg-atelier-surface w-full max-w-[320px] mx-auto h-[520px] overflow-hidden relative">
          <!-- Screen Header -->
          <div class="px-6 pt-8 pb-3 bg-atelier-surface">
            <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-atelier-onSurface tracking-tight">Collected Fragments</h2>
            <p class="text-xs text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant/80 mt-1">Your daily thoughts and captures</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Cards -->
          <div class="px-4 space-y-2.5 overflow-y-auto h-full pb-20 scrollbar-hide">
            <!-- Card 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card flex overflow-hidden active:scale-[0.99] transition-transform">
              <div class="w-[3px] bg-atelier-primaryFixed rounded-l-2xl"></div>
              <div class="flex-1 px-4 py-3.5">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-atelier-onSurface truncate">Morning reflection</h4>
                  <span class="text-[11px] text-atelier-outlineVariant shrink-0">2h ago</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[13px] text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant mt-1.5 leading-[1.45] line-clamp-2">
                  The light through the window felt different today. It reminded me of summers...
                </p>
                <div class="mt-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-xs text-atelier-forest/70">#journal</span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-atelier-forest/70">#morning</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Card 2 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card flex overflow-hidden active:scale-[0.99] transition-transform">
              <div class="w-[3px] bg-atelier-primaryFixed rounded-l-2xl"></div>
              <div class="flex-1 px-4 py-3.5">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-atelier-onSurface truncate">Book notes: Atomic Habits</h4>
                  <span class="text-[11px] text-atelier-outlineVariant shrink-0">5h ago</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[13px] text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant mt-1.5 leading-[1.45] line-clamp-2">
                  Small changes compound over time. Identity-based habits are more sustainable...
                </p>
                <div class="mt-2 flex items-center justify-between">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-xs text-atelier-forest/70">#reading</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-0.5 text-atelier-outlineVariant">
                    <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15.172 7l-6.586 6.586a2 2 0 102.828 2.828l6.414-6.586a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-6.415 6.585a6 6 0 108.486 8.486L20.5 13"></path></svg>
                    <span class="text-[11px]">2</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Card 3 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card flex overflow-hidden active:scale-[0.99] transition-transform opacity-80">
              <div class="w-[3px] bg-atelier-primaryFixed rounded-l-2xl"></div>
              <div class="flex-1 px-4 py-3.5">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-atelier-onSurface truncate">Project ideation</h4>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-1 shrink-0">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full border-2 border-atelier-lime border-t-transparent animate-spin"></div>
                    <span class="text-[11px] text-atelier-outlineVariant">processing</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[13px] text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant mt-1.5 leading-[1.45] line-clamp-2">
                  What if the second brain could feel like a garden instead of a filing cabinet?
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant max-w-[320px] mx-auto">
          <p><strong>特点：</strong>极简、干净，信息层级清晰。</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-atelier-outlineVariant">缺点：所有卡片视觉趋同，缺乏情感温度和快速识别性。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2. Soft Pastel -->
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-atelier-forest">02. Soft Pastel</h3>
          <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-rose-50 text-rose-600">情感化</span>
        </div>
        <div class="phone-frame rounded-[40px] border-[8px] border-white bg-atelier-surface w-full max-w-[320px] mx-auto h-[520px] overflow-hidden relative">
          <div class="px-6 pt-8 pb-3 bg-atelier-surface">
            <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-atelier-onSurface tracking-tight">Collected Fragments</h2>
            <p class="text-xs text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant/80 mt-1">Color by mood</p>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 space-y-2.5 overflow-y-auto h-full pb-20 scrollbar-hide">
            <!-- Card 1: warm cream -->
            <div class="bg-[#fdf6e3] rounded-2xl shadow-card flex overflow-hidden active:scale-[0.99] transition-transform border border-[#f0e6cc]">
              <div class="w-[4px] bg-[#e6c875] rounded-l-2xl"></div>
              <div class="flex-1 px-4 py-3.5">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-atelier-onSurface truncate">Morning reflection</h4>
                  <span class="text-[11px] text-atelier-outlineVariant shrink-0">2h ago</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[13px] text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant mt-1.5 leading-[1.45] line-clamp-2">
                  The light through the window felt different today. It reminded me of summers...
                </p>
                <div class="mt-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/70 text-[#8b7355]">#journal</span>
                  <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/70 text-[#8b7355]">#morning</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Card 2: soft blue -->
            <div class="bg-[#eef4fb] rounded-2xl shadow-card flex overflow-hidden active:scale-[0.99] transition-transform border border-[#d6e3f3]">
              <div class="w-[4px] bg-[#8ab4e6] rounded-l-2xl"></div>
              <div class="flex-1 px-4 py-3.5">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-atelier-onSurface truncate">Book notes: Atomic Habits</h4>
                  <span class="text-[11px] text-atelier-outlineVariant shrink-0">5h ago</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[13px] text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant mt-1.5 leading-[1.45] line-clamp-2">
                  Small changes compound over time. Identity-based habits are more sustainable...
                </p>
                <div class="mt-2 flex items-center justify-between">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/70 text-[#4a6fa5]">#reading</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-0.5 text-atelier-outlineVariant">
                    <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15.172 7l-6.586 6.586a2 2 0 102.828 2.828l6.414-6.586a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-6.415 6.585a6 6 0 108.486 8.486L20.5 13"></path></svg>
                    <span class="text-[11px]">2</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Card 3: soft sage -->
            <div class="bg-[#f0f5f0] rounded-2xl shadow-card flex overflow-hidden active:scale-[0.99] transition-transform border border-[#d8e5d8]">
              <div class="w-[4px] bg-[#a3c9a8] rounded-l-2xl"></div>
              <div class="flex-1 px-4 py-3.5">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-atelier-onSurface truncate">Project ideation</h4>
                  <span class="text-[11px] text-atelier-outlineVariant shrink-0">1d ago</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[13px] text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant mt-1.5 leading-[1.45] line-clamp-2">
                  What if the second brain could feel like a garden instead of a filing cabinet?
                </p>
                <div class="mt-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/70 text-[#5a7d5f]">#ideas</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant max-w-[320px] mx-auto">
          <p><strong>特点：</strong>卡片背景根据内容情绪赋予低饱和度马卡龙色。</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-atelier-outlineVariant">温暖、亲切，适合日记类产品；但颜色过多可能稍显杂乱。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 3. Gradient Edge -->
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-atelier-forest">03. Gradient Edge</h3>
          <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-gradient-to-r from-atelier-forest to-atelier-lime text-white">现代感</span>
        </div>
        <div class="phone-frame rounded-[40px] border-[8px] border-white bg-atelier-surface w-full max-w-[320px] mx-auto h-[520px] overflow-hidden relative">
          <div class="px-6 pt-8 pb-3 bg-atelier-surface">
            <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-atelier-onSurface tracking-tight">Collected Fragments</h2>
            <p class="text-xs text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant/80 mt-1">Fluid & dynamic</p>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 space-y-2.5 overflow-y-auto h-full pb-20 scrollbar-hide">
            <!-- Card 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card flex overflow-hidden active:scale-[0.99] transition-transform">
              <div class="w-1.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-atelier-forest via-atelier-lime to-atelier-forest/20 rounded-l-2xl"></div>
              <div class="flex-1 px-4 py-3.5">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-atelier-onSurface truncate">Morning reflection</h4>
                  <span class="text-[11px] text-atelier-outlineVariant shrink-0">2h ago</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[13px] text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant mt-1.5 leading-[1.45] line-clamp-2">
                  The light through the window felt different today. It reminded me of summers...
                </p>
                <div class="mt-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-xs font-medium text-atelier-forest">#journal</span>
                  <span class="text-xs font-medium text-atelier-forest">#morning</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Card 2 -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-atelier-primaryFixed/30 rounded-2xl shadow-card flex overflow-hidden active:scale-[0.99] transition-transform border border-atelier-primaryFixed/50">
              <div class="w-1.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-atelier-forest via-atelier-lime to-atelier-forest/20 rounded-l-2xl"></div>
              <div class="flex-1 px-4 py-3.5">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-atelier-onSurface truncate">Book notes: Atomic Habits</h4>
                  <span class="text-[11px] text-atelier-outlineVariant shrink-0">5h ago</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[13px] text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant mt-1.5 leading-[1.45] line-clamp-2">
                  Small changes compound over time. Identity-based habits are more sustainable...
                </p>
                <div class="mt-2 flex items-center justify-between">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-xs font-medium text-atelier-forest">#reading</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-0.5 text-atelier-outlineVariant">
                    <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15.172 7l-6.586 6.586a2 2 0 102.828 2.828l6.414-6.586a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-6.415 6.585a6 6 0 108.486 8.486L20.5 13"></path></svg>
                    <span class="text-[11px]">2</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Card 3 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card flex overflow-hidden active:scale-[0.99] transition-transform">
              <div class="w-1.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-atelier-forest via-atelier-lime to-atelier-forest/20 rounded-l-2xl"></div>
              <div class="flex-1 px-4 py-3.5">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-atelier-onSurface truncate">Project ideation</h4>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-1 shrink-0">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full border-2 border-atelier-lime border-t-transparent animate-spin"></div>
                    <span class="text-[11px] text-atelier-outlineVariant">processing</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[13px] text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant mt-1.5 leading-[1.45] line-clamp-2">
                  What if the second brain could feel like a garden instead of a filing cabinet?
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant max-w-[320px] mx-auto">
          <p><strong>特点：</strong>左侧条使用品牌森林绿到黄绿的渐变，部分卡片背景也有微渐变。</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-atelier-outlineVariant">极具品牌辨识度，现代感强；渐变实现需注意性能。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 4. Glassmorphism -->
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-atelier-forest">04. Glassmorphism</h3>
          <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-white/60 text-atelier-forest border border-white/40">前卫</span>
        </div>
        <div class="phone-frame rounded-[40px] border-[8px] border-white w-full max-w-[320px] mx-auto h-[520px] overflow-hidden relative"
             style="background: linear-gradient(160deg, #e8f5e9 0%, #c8e6c9 40%, #a5d6a7 100%);">
          <div class="px-6 pt-8 pb-3">
            <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-atelier-forest tracking-tight">Collected Fragments</h2>
            <p class="text-xs text-atelier-forest/70 mt-1">Light & airy</p>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 space-y-3 overflow-y-auto h-full pb-20 scrollbar-hide">
            <!-- Card 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl shadow-glass flex overflow-hidden active:scale-[0.99] transition-transform border border-white/60">
              <div class="w-1 bg-white/80 rounded-l-2xl"></div>
              <div class="flex-1 px-4 py-3.5">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-atelier-forest truncate">Morning reflection</h4>
                  <span class="text-[11px] text-atelier-forest/60 shrink-0">2h ago</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[13px] text-atelier-forest/80 mt-1.5 leading-[1.45] line-clamp-2">
                  The light through the window felt different today. It reminded me of summers...
                </p>
                <div class="mt-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/50 text-atelier-forest border border-white/60">#journal</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Card 2 -->
            <div class="bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl shadow-glass flex overflow-hidden active:scale-[0.99] transition-transform border border-white/60">
              <div class="w-1 bg-white/80 rounded-l-2xl"></div>
              <div class="flex-1 px-4 py-3.5">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-atelier-forest truncate">Book notes: Atomic Habits</h4>
                  <span class="text-[11px] text-atelier-forest/60 shrink-0">5h ago</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[13px] text-atelier-forest/80 mt-1.5 leading-[1.45] line-clamp-2">
                  Small changes compound over time. Identity-based habits are more sustainable...
                </p>
                <div class="mt-2 flex items-center justify-between">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/50 text-atelier-forest border border-white/60">#reading</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-0.5 text-atelier-forest/60">
                    <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15.172 7l-6.586 6.586a2 2 0 102.828 2.828l6.414-6.586a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-6.415 6.585a6 6 0 108.486 8.486L20.5 13"></path></svg>
                    <span class="text-[11px]">2</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Card 3 -->
            <div class="bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl shadow-glass flex overflow-hidden active:scale-[0.99] transition-transform border border-white/60">
              <div class="w-1 bg-white/80 rounded-l-2xl"></div>
              <div class="flex-1 px-4 py-3.5">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-atelier-forest truncate">Project ideation</h4>
                  <span class="text-[11px] text-atelier-forest/60 shrink-0">1d ago</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[13px] text-atelier-forest/80 mt-1.5 leading-[1.45] line-clamp-2">
                  What if the second brain could feel like a garden instead of a filing cabinet?
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-atelier-onSurfaceVariant max-w-[320px] mx-auto">
          <p><strong>特点：</strong>半透明毛玻璃质感，背景色透过卡片若隐若现。</p>
